en_683281_1	The men were in police detention and were taken back to the scene of the crime in the early hours of today.
en_683281_2	The suspects were shot when they tried to steal the officers’ guns and escape.
en_683281_3	The 27-year-old victim’s charred remains were discovered last Thursday leading to outrage and protests over alleged police inaction.
